sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/SDK
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as TrainJob Controller<br/>opendatahub namespace
    participant JobSetCtl as JobSet Controller
    participant Scheduler as Scheduler<br/>(Volcano/Coscheduling)
    participant Pods as Training Pods<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: TrainJob Creation

    User->>API: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    API->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-*<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>API: Validation response
    API->>Controller: Watch event<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>API: GET TrainingRuntime<br/>ServiceAccount token
    API-->>Controller: Runtime template
    Controller->>API: CREATE JobSet<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>API: CREATE PodGroup<br/>ServiceAccount token (optional)
    Controller->>API: CREATE NetworkPolicy<br/>ServiceAccount token (RHOAI)
    API-->>Controller: Resources created

    Note over JobSetCtl,Scheduler: Flow 2: Gang Scheduling

    JobSetCtl->>API: Watch JobSet
    API-->>JobSetCtl: JobSet created event
    JobSetCtl->>API: CREATE Jobs
    Scheduler->>API: Watch PodGroup
    Scheduler->>Scheduler: All-or-nothing scheduling decision
    Scheduler->>Pods: Schedule all pods atomically

    Note over Pods,Storage: Flow 3: Training Execution

    Pods->>Storage: GET model artifacts<br/>AWS IAM auth
    Storage-->>Pods: Model files
    Pods->>Storage: GET dataset<br/>AWS IAM auth
    Storage-->>Pods: Dataset files
    Pods->>Pods: NCCL/MPI all-reduce<br/>Inter-pod TCP
    Pods->>Storage: PUT checkpoints<br/>AWS IAM auth

    Note over Controller,Pods: Flow 4: Progression Tracking (RHOAI)

    Controller->>API: GET Pods (list)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    API-->>Controller: Pod IPs
    Controller->>Pods: GET /metrics<br/>NetworkPolicy restricted
    Pods-->>Controller: JSON metrics<br/>{progressPercentage, currentStep, loss}
    Controller->>API: PATCH TrainJob annotation<br/>trainerStatus update
    API-->>Controller: Updated
